### Create a ticket
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "subject": "Example login issue",
  "description": "Customer cannot log in after password reset. The reset link appears to expire immediately.",
  "customerEmail": "user@example.com"
}

### Get a ticket by id
# Replace {{id}} with the returned UUID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/{{id}}
Accept: application/json

### List tickets (filter by status)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?status=NEW&page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### Update ticket status
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/{{id}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "TRIAGED",
  "allowRollback": false
}
